data.description: This immaculate home is located in a beautiful over 55 community in charming Barnegat. Amazing value for this gorgeous totally renovated home , club house, pool and tennis courts. This huge corner property features: All bamboo wood walnut finished flooring, Tuscan inspired kitchen with 42 inch walnut cabinets, crown moldings, tiled back splash, new appliances including a 5 burner gas convection oven, 3 door refrigerator, custom in kitchen desk area with large pantry and new washer & dryer, an open floor plan, solarium facing a private wooded area, Central AC , forced hot air, recirculating thermostat controlled ventless gas heater, 2 large bedrooms, walk -in closets, 2 updated and tiled full bathrooms, separate dining area, oversized garage, patio, awing, SOLAR panels, emergency generator, and irrigation system. The master bedroom is spacious with an appointed private full  bath which features: glass enclosed shower, double sink, granite top, tiled flooring and custom cabinet and linen cabinet .  Plenty of closets and storage. The garage has an interior entrance and a garage door opener. A short drive to the bay beaches or LBI with its famous white sandy beaches, lighthouse, restaurants, and fun filled activities.
